{
  "stem": "13315.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, actually-- Not until the Nazis came into Vienna, because most of my friends and fellows were non-Jewish-- girls as well as boys.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So until then, I felt very little of it, naturally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, and then I heard from somebody-- like, let's say I went with a girl when I was 16, 17, or so-- she said something about Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, what do you want?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You don't want to go with me?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, you are different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was the-- the value that she was telling you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not a value.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was actually more the-- how should I call it-- psychologically.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a psychological, environmental effect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She didn't say very much because I stopped her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, that was the Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were also a human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not on the Viennese Jews, you see, because-- and [? that ?] was [? the ?] pity for the eastern Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were exposed to all the negative aspects much more through than the Viennese Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why to me, later on, when Hitler-- he wasn't still in Austria, but in Germany-- some of the people I knew, students and so, who were belonging to the Nazi Party, which I found  out later.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, to you Viennese Jews, nothing will happen-- we are only after the eastern Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, don't kid me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You'll start with them, and you'll end up with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was very outspoken about those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was altogether different, because it wasn't that so much that the population at large was anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
